					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="4 DIY Marketing Tips for Empty-Wallet Entrepreneurs" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/1394220831-5-key-factors-website-success.jpg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
